246
00:24:23,119 --> 00:24:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] što mladi par može raditi

247
00:24:25,539 --> 00:24:26,839
[SPEAKER_00] u slobodno vrijeme, na primjer.

248
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:28,859
[SPEAKER_01] Što tebi znači vjera?

249
00:24:28,859 --> 00:24:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ti je toliko bilo bitno

250
00:24:31,519 --> 00:24:34,019
