256
00:24:43,660 --> 00:24:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] tako će ti se razvijati dalje i život

257
00:24:45,140 --> 00:24:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] i barem bi tako možda ti ja

258
00:24:46,319 --> 00:24:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] da ti se razvija život.

259
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je, mislim, ja sam odrasta

260
00:24:49,539 --> 00:24:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] nekako u vjeri,

261
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:53,279
