285
00:25:33,380 --> 00:25:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] reći svoje misli

286
00:25:34,980 --> 00:25:37,359
[SPEAKER_00] i neočekivati ništa za uzvrat,

287
00:25:37,359 --> 00:25:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego samo da ti neko bude tu kao,

288
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,799
