298
00:25:57,359 --> 00:25:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom,

299
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,859
[SPEAKER_00] jer u tim situacijama

300
00:25:59,859 --> 00:26:01,000
