306
00:26:10,039 --> 00:26:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Sad se ne mogu sjetiti.

307
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da ne, čak.

308
00:26:12,819 --> 00:26:15,220
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je napisa

309
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:16,200
