343
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] di ti je nada,

344
00:27:13,279 --> 00:27:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] di ti je vjera,

345
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] znaš da si u Božem prisustvu,

346
00:27:15,519 --> 00:27:18,359
[SPEAKER_00] sve što kontrira tome

347
00:27:18,359 --> 00:27:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] ne dolazi od gore

348
00:27:20,839 --> 00:27:22,240
[SPEAKER_00] i smatram da bi trebalo

349
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,759
