350
00:27:23,759 --> 00:27:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] samo kažem.

351
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] Te zamke zloga su danas jako česte

352
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:30,640
