360
00:27:43,339 --> 00:27:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] nego je jednostavno razgovor zbogu,

361
00:27:44,539 --> 00:27:45,799
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu da ti svoje misli

362
00:27:45,799 --> 00:27:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] njemu kažeš

363
00:27:47,460 --> 00:27:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] naglas u sebi

364
00:27:48,940 --> 00:27:51,420
