371
00:27:59,740 --> 00:28:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] Neko nema ni to.

372
00:28:01,980 --> 00:28:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] I onda nekako kad ideš kroz život,

373
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:06,279
