386
00:28:32,599 --> 00:28:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] i može krivo skrenjeti,

387
00:28:33,599 --> 00:28:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali uvijek se, znači,

388
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:35,859
[SPEAKER_00] Boguvi prašta.

389
00:28:35,859 --> 00:28:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] A koja je najveća zamka zloga?

390
00:28:38,079 --> 00:28:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pogotovo za tvoju generaciju,

391
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] ti si skoro deset godina mlađa od mene,

392
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:44,240
[SPEAKER_01] predstavljaš Gen Z, jel tako?

393
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:44,720
[SPEAKER_00] Mhm.

394
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:46,240
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je vama,

395
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:49,079
[SPEAKER_01] što ti se čini ovako najveća zamka?

396
00:28:49,079 --> 00:28:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Su li to društvene mreže?

397
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,960
