406
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:13,859
[SPEAKER_00] da neko drugi ima nešto što ti nemaš.

407
00:29:13,859 --> 00:29:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ima te tu, znači,

408
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,720
[SPEAKER_00] isto onako stopirati

409
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] i onako stati,

410
00:29:18,019 --> 00:29:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ja nemam nešto što on ima,

411
00:29:20,119 --> 00:29:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] što je naprave da to postigne

412
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,799
[SPEAKER_00] i zašto ja to ne mogu napraviti.

413
00:29:23,799 --> 00:29:25,180
[SPEAKER_00] I onda opet,

414
00:29:25,180 --> 00:29:27,359
[SPEAKER_00] dobro je kad neko to zna

415
00:29:27,359 --> 00:29:28,700
[SPEAKER_00] iskoristiti kao motivaciju za dalje.

416
00:29:28,700 --> 00:29:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad te to nekako zaustavi

417
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:34,240
[SPEAKER_00] da se misliš

418
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] kome ti pripadaš

419
00:29:36,180 --> 00:29:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] i za što se zalažeš,

420
00:29:38,140 --> 00:29:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] koja je tvoja uloga u ovom životu,

421
00:29:40,140 --> 00:29:41,740
[SPEAKER_00] znači, zna se čovjek često iskupiti.

422
00:29:41,740 --> 00:29:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo danas, kažem,

423
00:29:42,539 --> 00:29:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] mladi u ovim vremenima,

424
00:29:44,539 --> 00:29:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] kad ti je sve nekako lako dostupno,

425
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] te društvene mreže

426
00:29:49,299 --> 00:29:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] vidiš samo najidealnije od svega,

427
00:29:52,119 --> 00:29:54,299
[SPEAKER_00] vidiš samo idealnu sliku svega.

428
00:29:54,299 --> 00:29:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] Misliš se, ono,

429
00:29:55,940 --> 00:29:56,839
[SPEAKER_00] di sam ja u svemu ovome,

430
00:29:56,839 --> 00:29:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] ko sam ja u svemu ovome,

431
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:58,779
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ja nemam,

432
00:29:58,779 --> 00:29:59,740
