436
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:06,819
[SPEAKER_00] a tek mi je, ne znam, 23 godine.

437
00:30:06,819 --> 00:30:08,339
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da misli da su mlade danas

438
00:30:08,339 --> 00:30:09,640
