441
00:30:15,319 --> 00:30:18,339
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se izbori s tim,

442
00:30:18,339 --> 00:30:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] nemo me to pitat.

443
00:30:19,279 --> 00:30:21,400
[SPEAKER_01] Još se boriš, ja?

